<li local-id=3D"9c7677d8-6732-4329-8744-98c0e58275e7">
<p local-id=3D"f89b1eb09551">Batch operations structure in Japan</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"59976f85-d9c2-475a-a417-ee139754728d">
<p local-id=3D"3d3d367344f6">Opportunities and constraints for transition</=
p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"4741c88b-5dc9-4f7d-9ba7-dcc309e31244">
<h2 local-id=3D"795a2347492e" id=3D"JapanBatch/MFTOpportunitiesMeetingNotes=
andKeyOutcomes-=E2=9C=85KeyOutcomes(ExecutiveSummary)">=E2=9C=85 Key Outcom=
es (Executive Summary)</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"2633274c-fb2e-41fb-8763-1ea1a1cc7640">
<li local-id=3D"ed5497b0-8200-44d1-b57c-d7fb9eb085d3">
<p local-id=3D"21068ed338aa"><strong>INFORMED:</strong> Current batch opera=
tions depend on a <strong>multi-vendor model</strong> (Geantec, Cognizant, =
Tech Mahindra) with fragmented ownership and processes. <a class=3D"externa=
l-link" href=3D"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4=
-8c11-6c7d37f35e93_f3178e31-dbcd-452a-ad6c-4a8fd0fe6dc8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780=
016842567?context=3D%7B%22contextType%22:%22chat%22%7D" rel=3D"nofollow">[B=
irger Fja...=E3=83=AB=EF=BC=89 in chat | Teams]</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78fe3326-3295-4a96-9cd2-8087972631d9">
<p local-id=3D"1ad30510b2e1"><strong>INFORMED:</strong> Technical and proce=
ss constraints exist for transition, requiring <strong>careful planning and=
 phased execution</strong>. <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://team=
s.microsoft.com/l/message/19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4-8c11-6c7d37f35e93_f3178e31-=
dbcd-452a-ad6c-4a8fd0fe6dc8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780016842567?context=3D%7B%22co=
ntextType%22:%22chat%22%7D" rel=3D"nofollow">[Birger Fja...=E3=83=AB=EF=BC=
=89 in chat | Teams]</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"75b62d9e-2697-47dc-9ca9-d004249e4eb1">
<p local-id=3D"c7c38290184c"><strong>ACCEPTED:</strong> Need for <strong>pa=
rallel monitoring setup in current year</strong> and <strong>formal transit=
ion next year</strong>. <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://teams.mi=
crosoft.com/l/message/19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4-8c11-6c7d37f35e93_f3178e31-dbcd=
-452a-ad6c-4a8fd0fe6dc8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780016842567?context=3D%7B%22contex=
tType%22:%22chat%22%7D" rel=3D"nofollow">[Birger Fja...=E3=83=AB=EF=BC=89 i=
n chat | Teams]</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba98f091-e145-4b17-8e97-49d431ccb555">
<p local-id=3D"79ad24de29e1"><strong>ACCEPTED:</strong> Priority focus on <=
strong>reducing delays in batch execution and file transfers (MFT)</strong>=
. <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/=
19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4-8c11-6c7d37f35e93_f3178e31-dbcd-452a-ad6c-4a8fd0fe6dc=
8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780016842567?context=3D%7B%22contextType%22:%22chat%22%7D=
" rel=3D"nofollow">[Birger Fja...=E3=83=AB=EF=BC=89 in chat | Teams]</a></p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"90ce44b4-7516-4b6c-b35f-33c8e7fdff73">
<p local-id=3D"ae8251b21e2e"><strong>DECIDED:</strong> Collect structured q=
uestions from teams to clarify <strong>manual batch processes and MFT uncer=
tainties</strong> prior to transition. <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"h=
ttps://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4-8c11-6c7d37f35e9=
3_f3178e31-dbcd-452a-ad6c-4a8fd0fe6dc8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780016842567?context=
=3D%7B%22contextType%22:%22chat%22%7D" rel=3D"nofollow">[Birger Fja...=E3=
=83=AB=EF=BC=89 in chat | Teams]</a></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4f781081-968f-43f7-9f97-3978fc5fb322">
<h2 local-id=3D"b5c19589af91" id=3D"JapanBatch/MFTOpportunitiesMeetingNotes=
andKeyOutcomes-=F0=9F=94=8DDiscussionSummary(Condensed)">=F0=9F=94=8D Discu=
ssion Summary (Condensed)</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"56ac6fac639c" id=3D"JapanBatch/MFTOpportunitiesMeetingNotes=
andKeyOutcomes-1.CurrentBatchOperationsLandscape">1. Current Batch Operatio=
ns Landscape</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"1d2592af-b7d3-47e0-97f4-0fe90c7dbf82">
<li local-id=3D"42f8b63e-e616-466f-9d0f-fe7491ba8e5a">
<p local-id=3D"63b64388d919">Reviewed <strong>existing vendor ecosystem</st=
rong> and operational responsibilities. <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"=
https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4-8c11-6c7d37f35e=
93_f3178e31-dbcd-452a-ad6c-4a8fd0fe6dc8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780016842567?contex=
t=3D%7B%22contextType%22:%22chat%22%7D" rel=3D"nofollow">[Birger Fja...=E3=
=83=AB=EF=BC=89 in chat | Teams]</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e738da4c-afa6-49fc-85a1-a1ab9c182d2e">
<p local-id=3D"d253de5c590f">Identified <strong>dependency on manual proces=
ses</strong> and distributed ownership.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5b3da885280a" id=3D"JapanBatch/MFTOpportunitiesMeetingNotes=
andKeyOutcomes-2.TransitionOpportunities&amp;Constraints">2. Transition Opp=
ortunities &amp; Constraints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"84f8903a-5466-4850-836f-d041bae47e44">
<li local-id=3D"5d876914-d3db-42ec-8b1b-19244ff76e39">
<p local-id=3D"4b3a3695919c">Opportunities:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2a0420dc-f545-426e-a43e-0b48a01ec53e">
<li local-id=3D"cd30ded1-b22b-463f-ac0f-12bb43bb2692">
<p local-id=3D"59077d064600">Standardization of batch operations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0758ccb0-439e-44ba-93db-79c3a37a461f">
<p local-id=3D"1f20c08d9dc3">Automation of repetitive/manual activities</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"7861ab1f-0f97-46d0-b1d2-7c053505883e">
<p local-id=3D"9d6a9fe6963e">Consolidation of ownership into regional teams=
 (GOCC/GBO)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"63e4b9ce-6712-4064-a1f1-194a0513bd15">
<p local-id=3D"b7033f454210">Constraints:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7bbf7756-db56-4ba3-ab8e-9b25c800c40b">
<li local-id=3D"da050ad2-4044-4ed9-9a90-6f4672aedd3d">
<p local-id=3D"0507dba63712">Timeline sensitivity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9bc01310-fe14-4bea-a084-aa3181cfb7f1">
<p local-id=3D"aff61d7bb125">Need for preparation across teams</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"15846f64-e178-4985-bd92-32eb5d5bf894">
<p local-id=3D"4f92cf77c7f2">Existing complexity in vendor and application =
structure <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/=
message/19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4-8c11-6c7d37f35e93_f3178e31-dbcd-452a-ad6c-4a8=
fd0fe6dc8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780016842567?context=3D%7B%22contextType%22:%22ch=
at%22%7D" rel=3D"nofollow">[Birger Fja...=E3=83=AB=EF=BC=89 in chat | Teams=
]</a></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5c1707e1cc1c" id=3D"JapanBatch/MFTOpportunitiesMeetingNotes=
andKeyOutcomes-3.TechnicalClarifications">3. Technical Clarifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ab9547d6-7006-49a3-a593-1c2ad4623d15">
<li local-id=3D"6b12be5e-0882-4ed1-8e34-ae38bc95b9b7">
<p local-id=3D"7df294957046">Confirmed:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"40084132-bccc-41c6-a501-473692a5745d">
<li local-id=3D"928da20b-817f-41a5-b8f8-836ad626a212">
<p local-id=3D"7c7a6c475670">Use of <strong>CA workload automation</strong>=
 for job execution and monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"20aaa866-409d-4cdb-94bd-917dbcc49f52">
<p local-id=3D"5e8fc1382255">Responsibility demarcation for monitoring acti=
vities</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"5e701969-e244-4163-ba52-ff4781456313">
<p local-id=3D"741ee7bf8488">Addressed:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b44beddc-f9b5-4f47-a33f-ddf42f28d33d">
<li local-id=3D"575177ba-fd4b-4fda-a70f-f68a2c0d152c">
<p local-id=3D"8c0b85c54732">Prior <strong>language barrier challenges</str=
ong> affecting coordination <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://team=
s.microsoft.com/l/message/19:8b44df3f-571b-40d4-8c11-6c7d37f35e93_f3178e31-=
dbcd-452a-ad6c-4a8fd0fe6dc8@unq.gbl.spaces/1780016842567?context=3D%7B%22co=
ntextType%22:%22chat%22%7D" rel=3D"nofollow">[Birger Fja...=E3=83=AB=EF=BC=
=89 in chat | Teams]</a></p></li>
</ul></li>
